<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / About</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="grid grid-2">
            <div>
                <img src="/images/fleet_cargo.png" alt="Logistics Operations" class="img-fluid radius-image">
            </div>
            <div class="about-details">
                <h4 class="sub-heading">OUR STORY</h4>
                <h2>Pioneering Transport in the UAE</h2>
                <p>At Tiger Youth Transport, we believe that logistics is the backbone of modern global trade. Based firmly in the trading hub of Dubai, we have strategically expanded our operations over the past decade to become a leading road freight and cargo service provider across the entire Gulf Cooperation Council (GCC).</p>
                <p>Our commitment to continuous technological adoption, rigorous fleet maintenance, and human capital development ensures that every dispatch is executed with surgical precision.</p>
                
                <h4 class="sub-heading mt-4">OUR MISSION</h4>
                <p>To deliver scalable, safe, and lightning-fast logistics solutions that empower businesses to thrive seamlessly across borders.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stats-row mt-6">
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span class="stat-number">15+</span>
                <span class="stat-text">Years Experience</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span class="stat-number">50K+</span>
                <span class="stat-text">Shipments Delivered</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span class="stat-number">300+</span>
                <span class="stat-text">Fleet Vehicles</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span class="stat-number">6</span>
                <span class="stat-text">GCC Countries</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-padding bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title text-center mb-5">
            <h2>Our <span class="highlight">Core Values</span></h2>
            <p>The principles that drive our logistics excellence and customer satisfaction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-3">
            <div class="value-card shadow-large">
                <div class="value-icon">&#128737;</div>
                <h3>Uncompromising Safety</h3>
                <p>We adhere closely to ISO and GCC traffic regulations, ensuring the safety of our drivers, cargo, and communities.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card shadow-large">
                <div class="value-icon">&#129309;</div>
                <h3>Complete Transparency</h3>
                <p>No hidden fees and full timeline visibility. You receive clear, upfront quotes and real-time tracking from dispatch to delivery.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card shadow-large">
                <div class="value-icon">&#128640;</div>
                <h3>Operational Speed</h3>
                <p>Time is money in logistics. We constantly optimize routes and border transitions to shave hours off standard transit times.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="grid grid-2 align-center">
            <div>
                <h4 class="sub-heading">THE TEAM BEHIND THE WHEEL</h4>
                <h2>Expert Logistics <span class="highlight">Professionals</span></h2>
                <p class="mb-4">Our operations run smoothly thanks to our highly trained personnel. From our seasoned compliance officers and customer support agents in Dubai to our vast network of certified, experienced drivers across the GCC—our people are our greatest strength.</p>
                
                <div class="certifications-banner mt-4">
                    <h4>Our Certifications & Compliance</h4>
                    <div class="cert-tags mt-3">
                        <span class="cert-tag">&#10003; ISO 9001:2015</span>
                        <span class="cert-tag">&#10003; GCC Transport Authority Approved</span>
                        <span class="cert-tag">&#10003; Hazmat Certified Fleet</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <img src="/images/team_cargo.png" alt="Tiger Youth Logistics Team" class="img-fluid radius-image shadow-large">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
